Package: BasicStatsHelper
Title: Simple Statistical Analysis Helper Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Turbo", "Du", , "turbodu@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides easy-to-use functions for common statistical analyses
    including descriptive statistics, confidence intervals, hypothesis testing,
    and data visualization helpers. Designed for students and researchers who
    need quick and reliable statistical computations with clear interpretations.
